Description:
Requirement for the provision of legal services to the Bank of England in connection with technology projects during 2022.
The scope of work is as follows:
•	advising on appropriate contractual structures;
•	drafting contractual terms and/or reviewing those proposed by suppliers;
•	advising on the procurement processes involved;
•	reviewing procurement documents such as SQs, ITTs, ITPDs, etc.;
•	dealing with ad hoc legal queries from the Bank and opposing legal counsel throughout.

Renewal of VIP Select portal including the following Adobe Apps used across the Maritime and Coastguard Agency:

Adobe Creative Cloud All Apps is a full creative software suite for professional editing, this is used throughout the Agency (primarily by the Press Office) for industry-standard image and video;
Adobe Captivate allows the recording of videos to the best standard, this is used to create training videos;
Adobe Pro allows users to edit and create PDFs, required by many business areas.

This opportunity was a Further Competition run under Crown Commercial Services RM6068 framework, open to all Lot 3 suppliers.
